title: Break Yourself to Remake Yourself
itunes:title: Break Yourself to Remake Yourself
description:
Episode 592 - Are you stuck in a comfort zone? The only way to get out of that comfort zone is to get to a breaking point where you want to give up and push through it. You have to break yourself down so that your old self is completely unrecognizable and then rebuild yourself into the person that you want to be. Check out this episode to learn more. If you are ready to break out of your comfort zones, join my Iron Mind 60 challenge at www.IronMind60.com
